snippet.title: Gingerlocks
snippet.description:
I'm GingerLocks 🌻🌻.  I deal with over 5 different auto immune issues, and unfortunately I'm unable to work.  I started this channel a year ago, to help and educate about Chronic Illness. I LOVE the Philadelphia Eagles & The Dave Matthews Band!  I'm trying to live my life to the fullest and this also helps me because I'm disabled ...YOU DON'T always need to stay home!  Go out and enjoy life...it's hard...I just hope I can help!  My channel is about trying to be about trying to stay positive and learn how to deal with the "Bad days".  I was also a reporter back in the day, I enjoy True Crime & Celebrity Gossip!   Let's take this journey together!

Contact me at GingerLocks2020@gmail.com
